To create a self signed cert -

1. Install openssl
yum install -y openssl

2. Run the below command to generate the key and certificate in pem format
openssl req -newkey rsa:2048 -nodes -keyout key.pem -x509 -days 730 -out certificate.pem

3.  Install it on the LBaaS.

4.  Install it as trusted cert in your cert store.
